{"tid":665801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一度被斥淫穢　《向左側臥的裸女》成蘇富比最貴藝術品","createTime":"2018-05-15T09:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T05:24:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"10da4b81240176e0fa5dbb70d6511fa1615a24c2","tid":665801,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180515/s00005/dde8b5a7f2d5080d020d0629511c2c69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180515%2Fs00005%2Fdde8b5a7f2d5080d020d0629511c2c69.jpg&h=2bec408b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n著名意大利畫家莫迪利安尼（Amedeo Modigliani）畫作《向左側臥的裸女》，成為拍賣行蘇富比史上成交價最高的藝術品。這幅畫作在20世紀初，曾被視為淫穢物品，當年引起極大爭議。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪利安尼在1917年創作的畫作《向左側臥的裸女》 （Nu couch&eacute; (sur le c&ocirc;t&eacute; gauche)）於周一（14日）在紐約蘇富比拍賣會，以1.57億美元（約12.4億港元）成交，創下蘇富比有史以來最高的拍賣價。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪利安尼另一幅1917年著名作品《側臥的裸女》（Nu couch&eacute;），在2015年的佳士得紐約拍賣會，以1.7億美元（約13.1億港元）成交，當時亦打破了莫迪利安尼油畫的成交紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n在1916至1919年期間，莫迪利安尼共創作22幅裸女畫作。畫作首次公開時引起極大爭議，由於法國警察視畫作為淫穢物品，莫迪利安尼一個畫展，在開幕後數小時被迫關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180515/s00005/1526374199144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180515%2Fs00005%2F1526374199144&d=fPrERKXOLSGnjnJt4dppowRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4fa77e0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180515%2Fs00005%2F1526374199144&h=6776fd7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180515/s00005/1526374199144</a>"},{"pid":"47b8178ec516968001610f11be8311fd18bfe823","tid":665801,"uid":102096,"like":172,"dislike":10,"score":162,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"043af34cffcf671578cf4354b933cacd0a9c0e1f","tid":665801,"uid":64009,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":